  sugar: 8 g
  protein: 35 g
  fiber: 3 g
  sodium: 910 mg
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/sunday-dinner-chicken-gravy-61f187ada5c2791f5c0e9583
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
